times ahead for Steve Ortmayer who was, indeed, fired Monday as director of 
football operations. ; Photo, Steve Ortmayer, fired Monday by the Chargers as 
director of football operations, is looking for a job. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
