<P>
Photo, Colorado State center Eric Friehauf dunks the ball as Cal State 
Fullerton's Aaron Wilhite watches. ; Photo, Easy basket -- Cal State 
Fullerton's Cedric Ceballos shoots over Mark Meredith to score two of his 14 
points. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
