<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Eugene H. DeFalco has resigned from WD-40 Co.'s board of directors after 21 
years service. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
